com.alexkasko.unsafe.offheap
Class OffHeapBinarySearch.IndexRange

java.lang.Object
  com.alexkasko.unsafe.offheap.OffHeapBinarySearch.IndexRange
Enclosing class:
OffHeapBinarySearch
public static class OffHeapBinarySearch.IndexRange
extends Object

OffHeapAddressable index range representation. isEmpty() method should be checked before accessing indices. Empty range will contain negative equal indices which values are -index - 1 where the element would be inserted. Range with size 1 will contain equal indices.
